description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity to join our friendly and professional lifeguarding team as a Leisure Assistant here at Odstock Health and Fitness with both permanent and bank positions available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will work to provide a safe and enjoyable swimming experience for all our members and guests, assist with customer focused reception duties and help to issue memberships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A current NPLQ qualification is required for the post and logged training hours if applicable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sally Crook Centre Coordinator&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;sally.crook@nhs.net 01722 425085&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kirsty Purdon - Pool Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
